1
00:00:00,333 --> 00:00:02,916
My name is Muhammad Nour Shahadah,
I reside in the city of Tabqa

2
00:00:03,750 --> 00:00:05,791
I am 31 years old, born in 1990

3
00:00:06,875 --> 00:00:08,750
I was detained in 2017

4
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:11,833
I am married and have 4 children

5
00:00:12,291 --> 00:00:15,750
I was detained and taken from my home
at exactly 10:00 in the morning

6
00:00:16,625 --> 00:00:18,166
I do not remember the exact day of the month

7
00:00:18,708 --> 00:00:22,541
A patrol of ISIS members came to me
and detained me from my home, blindfolded

8
00:00:23,208 --> 00:00:26,125
Being from the city of Tabqa, I knew they took me
to Bourj [Tower] Prison

9
00:00:26,625 --> 00:00:28,708
Based on my estimation of the directions
they took

10
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:32,166
As soon as I arrived here,
I was imprisoned

11
00:00:32,625 --> 00:00:35,791
The car drove us in here,
and then we walked

12
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:37,916
They brought me down approximately here

13
00:00:38,750 --> 00:00:39,750
Right here

14
00:00:40,208 --> 00:00:45,125
They grabbed me by my hair like this,
pulling my head back, and walked me forward

15
00:00:46,583 --> 00:00:50,833
Then they took me to a room,
I do not know exactly where it was

16
00:00:51,708 --> 00:00:55,208
I took off my shoes, pardon me,
and then went inside

17
00:00:56,750 --> 00:01:01,208
They took my personal information,
then led me to a group cell, a small room

18
00:01:01,375 --> 00:01:02,416
Its dimensions were roughly

19
00:01:03,541 --> 00:01:06,000
Half a meter wide, or slightly more, 60 cm

20
00:01:06,791 --> 00:01:10,833
Two meters long,
the length of a grown man

21
00:01:12,583 --> 00:01:13,750
It was called the disciplinary cell

22
00:01:14,166 --> 00:01:18,625
One of the ISIS members, after taking my
personal information, struck me here on my cheek

23
00:01:19,041 --> 00:01:22,958
Which broke the bone here and left a visible mark,
then he ordered the others to take me to disciplinary

24
00:01:23,541 --> 00:01:27,625
The vehicle was a Hyundai H1,
and they blindfolded me inside it

25
00:01:28,666 --> 00:01:29,791
A small passenger van, a Hyundai

26
00:01:29,833 --> 00:01:33,916
When we entered here, I heard the sound
of the car tires over that metal rail

27
00:01:34,750 --> 00:01:37,375
So I immediately knew they had brought me
to Bourj Prison

28
00:01:38,041 --> 00:01:39,041
We entered from here

29
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:41,375
I was blindfolded,
so one of them grabbed me by my hair

30
00:01:41,708 --> 00:01:43,833
At the time my hair was longer,
so he grabbed me from behind like this

31
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:45,333
And walked me forward

32
00:01:46,333 --> 00:01:47,333
We entered like this

33
00:01:47,791 --> 00:01:53,250
And of course, when you enter here,
they start beating you and filling you with fear and terror

34
00:01:53,875 --> 00:01:55,583
As if you are walking to your death

